    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor shortfalls at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package under a limited-scope authorization pending resolution of six epistemic gaps. The Monte Carlo UQ framework, while incomplete, demonstrates partial uncertainty coverage. Conditional acceptance is granted with mandatory follow-up actions to address model form, test samples, and equivalency factors prior to regulatory submission. The inline requirement object documenting these conditions is embedded in the package description narrative; formal bindsRequirement linkage is pending administrative completion.",
